BBEX3.D.BGN.USD.CA.AC.000: Exchange rates for the US dollar in Bulgaria / USD 1 = BGN ... (middle)

General: A currency conversion at the rate of BGL 1,000 = BGN 1 took place on 5 July 1999; the BGL remained legal tender at this rate until 31 December 1999. The rates for 1 and 2 July 1999 were converted at the rate mentioned above.
